T02D1440:239b-1: shr'i tsakra samba ra sto tra:/
T02D1440:239b-3: dpal 'khor lo sdom pa'i bstod pa /
T02D1440:239b-4: dpal bde mchog 'khor lo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-5: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad cing //
T02D1440:239b-6: chos dbyings rnam dag ye shes ngo bo nyid //
T02D1440:239b-7: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma dang mnyam par sbyor //
T02D1440:239b-8: zhe sdang rdo rje khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-9: h'um gi rdo rje lam byung char sprin mdog / dga' ba rnam dag drag po'i zhal bzhir snang //
T02D1440:239b-10: gar gyi nyams dgus gdul dka' 'dul mdzad pa //
T02D1440:239b-11: h'um mdzad rdo rje khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-12: rten 'brel bcu gnyis dag pas sa rnams rdzogs //
T02D1440:239b-13: bcu gnyis phyag gis phyag mchan sna tshogs 'dzin //
T02D1440:239b-14: yul dang yul can rnam rtog 'joms mdzad pa'i //
T02D1440:239b-15: ngo mtshang mtshon cha bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-16: h'um gi nga ros srid gsum skrag mdzad cing //
T02D1440:239b-17: rngam pa'i rkan sgra phat kyi sgra sgrogs pas //
T02D1440:239b-18: bdud dang bgegs tshogs gdul dka' ma lus 'dul //
T02D1440:239b-19: rnam rtog bgegs bdud 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-20: spros bral bde mchog padma r'a ga'i mdog / stong nyid 'od gsal dus gsum bde gshegs blo //
T02D1440:239b-21: rnam rtog dra ba ma lus 'joms mdzad pa'i //
T02D1440:239b-22: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-23: sa chu me rlung 'byung ba rnam par dag / dag pa'i zhal bzhi rigs kyi yum du snang //
T02D1440:239b-24: dran pa nyer gzhag bzhi yi ngo bo nyid ;
T02D1440:239b-25: / mkha' 'gro ma sogs yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:239b-26: sems kyi rnam rtogs bla'i srid pa sbyong //
T02D1440:239b-27: zhe sdang rnam dag thugs kyi 'khor lor snang //
T02D1440:239b-28: thod pa'i dum bu rab gtum ma la sogs //
T02D1440:239b-29: gnas dang nye gnas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:240a-0: gsung gi nga ros sa stengs @240a * //
T02D1440:240a-2: 'dod chags rnam dag gsung gi 'khor lor snang //
T02D1440:240a-3: myu gu can dang sa srungs ma la sogs //
T02D1440:240a-4: zhing dang nye zhing rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:240a-5: sku yi rol pas sa 'og srid pa sbyong //
T02D1440:240a-6: gti mug rnam dag sku yi 'khor lor snang //
T02D1440:240a-7: stobs po che dang 'khor lo'i shugs can sogs //
T02D1440:240a-8: 'dus sogs gnas la bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:240a-9: yang dag las mtha' 'tsho ba rtsol dran //
T02D1440:240a-10: bde chen dga' ba mos dang gtso la phyogs //
T02D1440:240a-11: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus srung mdzad pa //
T02D1440:240a-12: sgo bzhi ma mor snang la phyag 'tshal lo ;
T02D1440:240a-13: / brtson 'grus rnam ngag yang dag spong ba bzhi //
T02D1440:240a-14: gshin rje brtan ma la sogs ma mor snang //
T02D1440:240a-15: phyogs gnyis 'dzin pas sku mdog phyed gzugs ma //
T02D1440:240a-16: rgyal ba'i yum du bstan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:240a-17: bde gshegs brgyad kyis bstan pa'i snying por bstan //
T02D1440:240a-18: bdag med dkyil 'khor dur khrod brgyad du gnas //
T02D1440:240a-19: byang chub rkyen du shing brgyad mngon du byung //
T02D1440:240a-20: 'jig rten chos brgyad bsregs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1440:240a-21: dpal 'khor lo sdom pa'i bstod pa /
